then terminate one of them when you learn the earnings), and require compan=
ies to *disclose* if their officers terminated any 10b5-1 plans, but they d=
on=E2=80=99t really prohibit terminating the plans, and it=E2=80=99s not cl=
ear how they could. They do require officers to certify that they are =E2=
=80=9Cadopting the plan in good faith and not as part of a plan or scheme t=
o evade the prohibitions of this section,=E2=80=9D but if you=E2=80=99re go=
ing to do this scheme presumably you would be willing to certify that.


